	  <persName key="pers:Ma-Pālitaṇaka">pālitaṇakasa</persName>
	  deyadhama leṇa koḍhi <unclear>ca</unclear>
	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
	<p>
	  Success! The religious gift of a cave and a cistern by 
	  <persName key="pers:Ma-Pālitaṇaka">Pālitaṇaka</persName>,
	  the minister of the Kāṇabhoa <persName key="pers:Ma-Viṣṇupālita">Viṣṇupālita</persName>.
	</p>
